    public class MemoryBrokerImpl
extends SwResourceImpl
implements MemoryBroker
    An implementation of the model object 'Memory Broker'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Access Policy
    • Memories
    • Memory Block Adress Elements
    • Memory Block Size Elements
    • Lock Services
    • Unlock Services
    • Map Services
    • Un Map Services
